featureType.title: Seamounts of Australia (Harris & Heap 2008)
featureType.abstract:
Seamount features were extracted from Heap, A.D., Harris, P.T. 2008. Geomorphology of the Australian Margin and Adjacent Seafloor. Geoscience Australia, Canberra. http://dx.doi.org/10.1080/08120090801888669
Minor edits (redigitisation of feature boundaries) were made for features in SE Australia based on newer bathymetry coverage.
